Description.Text: Grand 5 is a brand new addition to the Bangkok luxury hotel scene located on Sukhumvit Soi 5, just a few minutes' walk from the BTS Nana Station and the city's hidden Arab quarter. Not only does Grand 5 provide spacious and stylish accommodation for executive and leisure travelers, it is perfectly placed within a new shopping complex with coffee shops, supermarkets, fast food outlets, restaurants and retail outlets all under one roof!

After a long day of travelling, sightseeing or meetings, step inside the comforts of private guestroom and leave the stress of the city behind. This luxury Bangkok hotel is designed to relax and soothe the mind with neutral colors, a tranquil ambiance and modern facilities. Spread over nine floors, Grand 5 Hotel & Plaza offers 161 accommodations with city views in two distinct room types, the Deluxe and Grand Deluxe.

When it is time to escape the hustle and bustle of the city streets the soothing ambiance of this luxury hotel in Sukhumvit offers the ultimate respite. The mellow tones of the contemporary d√©cor are instantly calming and with a spa, spacious lobby, business center, restaurant and bar, it is easy to relax and indulge in warm hospitality and pampering services. The rooms and suites are larger than average, filled with high-tech amenities and with nine floors most rooms offer excellent cityscape views. Hotel also have a rejuvenating spa offering massages and spa treatments with a beauty salon.

To satisfy your appetite this spacious restaurant has a split level design with 150 seats and is open all day serving a delicious breakfast buffet in the morning and a la carte international dishes for lunch and dinner. The elegant bar is a focal point after dark with mellow music to help guests unwind.
